0c691885db3c8deb\"></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce982fa11d02831d33053808284030ab34aa303baaa5c7f90d1b847697ea724976f6534b2acf04d6a7bff002f5f586048d3db3c8deb\" style=\"clear:none;float:none;\" alt=\"78f3c028e2f206a26d81f6e64786776e1ca0\"></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce982fa11d02831d33053808284030ab34aa303baaa5c7f90d1b847697ea724976f6534b2acf04d6a7ba90a7d5f5f6c4f87db3c8deb\" style=\"clear:none;float:none;\" alt=\"viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce982fa11d02831d33053808284030ab34aa303baaa5c7f90d1b847697ea724976f6534b2acf04d6a7ba90a7d5f5f6c4f87db3c8deb\"></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce982fa11d02831d33053808284030ab34aa303baaa5c7f90d1b847697ea724976f6534b2acf04d6a7ba9567e565d604f81db3c8deb\" style=\"clear:none;float:none;\" alt=\"viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce982fa11d02831d33053808284030ab34aa303baaa5c7f90d1b847697ea724976f6534b2acf04d6a7ba9567e565d604f81db3c8deb\"></p><p><br></p><p></p><p><span style=\"font-size:10pt;\">연동 성공했으면 이제 디스코드로 돌아와서 CD-keys 채널에서 새로운 쿠1폰 코드 복붙해서</span></p><p style=\"max-width:100%;line-height:2;\">CDkey-redemption 채널에 있는 2번째 버튼 누르면 뜨는 창에 쿠1폰 코드 복붙해서 전송 버튼 누르면&nbsp;<br style=\"max-width:100%;\">Redemption Success 뜬다면 니케 인게임으로 성공적으로 보상이 전해진거임<br style=\"max-width:100%;\">만약 Failed 떳다면 코드 이상하게 입력했거나 또는 쿠1폰 만료 되었거나 기타 이유로 영어로 적어져서 너에게 알려줄거임</p><p><br></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce982fa11d02831d33053808284030ab34aa303baaa5c7f90d1b847697ea724976f6534b2acf04d6a7bfa042e5f0e681e86db3c8deb\" style=\"clear:none;float:none;\" alt=\"viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce982fa11d02831d33053808284030ab34aa303baaa5c7f90d1b847697ea724976f6534b2acf04d6a7bfa042e5f0e681e86db3c8deb\"></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce982fa11d02831d33053808284030ab34aa303baaa5c7f90d1b847697ea724976f6534b2acf04d6a7bff05290a086048d0db3c8deb\" style=\"clear:none;float:none;\" alt=\"viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce982fa11d02831d33053808284030ab34aa303baaa5c7f90d1b847697ea724976f6534b2acf04d6a7bff05290a086048d0db3c8deb\"></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce982fa11d02831d33053808284030ab34aa303baaa5c7f90d1b847697eca4a9f656436b1aff14d3074ea18f68a59d779b8c8ce79bf6f\" style=\"clear:none;float:none;\" alt=\"viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce982fa11d02831d33053808284030ab34aa303baaa5c7f90d1b847697eca4a9f656436b1aff14d3074ea18f68a59d779b8c8ce79bf6f\"></p><p><br></p><p></p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;\">성공적으로 되면 이제 쿠1폰 보상이 메일로 올거임.</span></p><br style=\"max-width:100%;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">참고로 니케 서버 또는 홈페이지가 불안정하면 쿠1폰 보상이 지연될수 있기 때문에 기다리면 온다고하니 만약 안왔다면 기다려주면 됨.</span><br style=\"max-width:100%;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br style=\"max-width:100%;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">이제 쿠1폰 뜰때마다 번거롭게 로딩 안기다리고 디스코드로 아주 빠르게 쿠1폰 코드만 복붙으로 딸깍 해서&nbsp;</span><br style=\"max-width:100%;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;\">보상 타먹고 즐거운 니케 플레이 하는레후</span><br><br><img class=\"written_dccon\" src=\"https://dcimg5.dcinside.com/dccon.php?no=62b5df2be09d3ca567b1c5bc12d46b394aa3b1058c6e4d0ca41648b650e9226efc5475f2b10a5199b36f890aebdd9af879163a7ef0f5a257454ae410ceb65851ed8334c6bda228d3\" conalt=\"085\" alt=\"085\" title=\"085\" data-dcconoverstatus=\"false\"><br><br></p><p></p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;\">-- 추가 --</span></p><br style=\"max-width:100%;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;\">디스코드 알림이 시도 때도 없이 온다면 이거 확인해보셈<br></span><br></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce982fa11d02831d33053808284030ab34aa303baaa5c7f90d1b847697eca4a9f656436b1aff14d3074ea1cff8c5ad979e3c9ce79bf6f\" style=\"clear:none;float:none;\" alt=\"7ced9e36ebd518986abce89544887064df\"></p><p style=\"text-align:left;\"><img src=\"https://dcimg1.dcinside.com/viewimage.php?id=2ab2c6&amp;no=24b0d769e1d32ca73ce982fa11d02831d33053808284030ab34aa303baaa5c7f90d1b847697eca4a9f656436b1aff14d3074ea14ff8805db7bba99ce79bf6f\" style=\"clear:none;float:none;\" alt=\"7cec9e36ebd518986abce895458774689b\"></p><p><br></p><p></p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;\">서버 리스트에 있는 니케 공식 서버 마우스 우클릭 누르면 목록 뜨는데 거기서 알림 설정 누르면 이렇게 딱 뜨는데&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">서버 알림 설정이 모든 메세지로 되있다면&nbsp;</span><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://arca.live/u/@mention%EB%A7%8C\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);max-width:100%;font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;\" target=\"_blank\">@mention만</a><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">&nbsp;으로 체크하면 너한테 직접 핑 찍거나&nbsp;</span><a class=\"lnk\" href=\"https://arca.live/u/@\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);max-width:100%;font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;\" target=\"_blank\">@</a><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">Everyone 찍는거 아니면 알림 더이상 안올거임.</span><br style=\"max-width:100%;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><br style=\"max-width:100%;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\">그리고 디스코드 처음 쓰는 게이들은 모르는 사람이 개인 메세지로 이상한 링크 같은거 보내면 누르지말고 차단 눌러라&nbsp;</span><br style=\"max-width:100%;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\"></p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:QANrPkTKkPzwQk1u4aWP, '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, NanumBarunGothic, 'system-ui', sans-serif;font-size:15px;\">십중팔구 스팸 이거나 해킹 당할수 있다</span><br></p>",
  "snippet": "글섭이나 북미섭, 동남아섭 협전 구하는 게이들은 보셈 - 니케 마이너 갤러리요즘 갤이나 옆동네에서 글섭, 북미섭, 동남아섭 협동전 인원 구하는글 많이 보이는데 서로 시간대 안맞아서 인원 풀로 못채우고 가는거 많이 보여서 올려봄일단 필요한건 디스코드임 앵간해서는 친구들끼리 겜 한다고 깔려있으면gall.dcinside.com디스코드 안 깔려있으면 위에 링크 타",
